<!--zh
- echarts.init 须在 window.onload（或 load 监听）内执行，禁止内联脚本解析阶段顶层 init；不要用 DOMContentLoaded 代替 load。
- onload 内 setOption 后须再异步 resize 一次（如双 requestAnimationFrame 或 setTimeout 0）；须监听 window.resize，对所有图表实例调用 resize()。
- 图表容器须有明确高度；饼图类若竖排 legend，须保证容器宽度或调整 legend，避免挤出。
- 绘图区须尽量占满容器：合理设置 grid（必要时 containLabel）、饼图/雷达等的 center 与 radius，在标签可读前提下减少四周无效留白。
多轴对齐：
- 同方向轴刻度数量一致，避免网格线错位；用 min、max、interval 对齐刻度
视觉要求：
- 坐标轴、网格线、标签对齐；避免重叠与过密；配色统一，不遮挡关键数据
-->
- Run echarts.init only inside window.onload (or load listener), not at top level while the inline script parses; do not use DOMContentLoaded instead of load.
- After setOption inside onload, schedule one async resize (e.g. double requestAnimationFrame or setTimeout 0); listen to window.resize and call resize() on every chart instance.
- Chart containers need explicit height; pie or doughnut with vertical legend needs enough width or adjusted legend to avoid overflow.
- Maximize plot area within the container: tune grid (use containLabel when needed), pie or radar center and radius, and margins so labels stay readable without large empty bands.
Multi-axis alignment:
- Same-direction axes: consistent tick counts; use min, max, interval to align ticks and avoid grid misalignment.
Visual requirements:
- Align axes, grid, labels; avoid overlap and clutter; cohesive colors, do not obscure key data.
